metadata.name: amusement of a cosmic puppeteer
metadata.description:
The boundaries of our own imagination and creativity doesn't exist. We have the power to shape our own realities, no matter how small or insignificant they may seem in the grand scheme of things. The cosmic background hints at the infinite possibilities that lie beyond our immediate perceptions, encouraging us to think beyond our own limited perspectives.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, Superchief Gallery NFT x Exquisite Workers.
